extends layout

block content
	p The purpose of this community is to educate, share experiences, post some saucy memes, and provide a resource for channels that are looking for quality moderators for their events and/or communities on Twitch.
	p We require some indication of current moderation experience in order to join. You must satisfy one of the following criteria:
	ul
		li You are a Twitch Partner #[img(src="https://static-cdn.jtvnw.net/badges/v1/d12a2e27-16f6-41d0-ab77-b780518f00a3/1" alt="(verified badge)")]
		li You are a Twitch Employee #[img(src="https://static-cdn.jtvnw.net/badges/v1/d97c37bd-a6f5-4c38-8f57-4e4bef88af34/1" alt="(employee badge)")]
		li The total number of followers on channels you moderate exceeds 15 000 #[em and] at least one of those channels is a Twitch Partner
	div
		a.account-link#discord(href=discord_url)= 'Get Started'